videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets fired up after he elevates to flush an and-1 alley-oop dunk on Ivica Zubac that sends the Suns crowd into a frenzy.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ayton's two-handed dunk ignites Suns' crowd) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ayton's two-handed dunk ignites Suns' crowd

videos.description: Cam Payne gets hyped up after knocking down a 3-pointer to put the Suns up 46-40 over the Clippers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Payne fired up after big 3) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Payne fired up after big 3

videos.description: Cam Payne fakes the Clippers defense and swoops in with a smooth finger roll to give the Suns a 59-54 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Cam Payne finesses in sweet finger roll) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cam Payne finesses in sweet finger roll

videos.description: Deandre Ayton puts the defense on notice as he emphatically throws down a two-handed dunk on the alley-oop pass from Devin Booker.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker lobs to Ayton for gigantic slam) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker lobs to Ayton for gigantic slam

videos.description: Devin Booker and Pat Beverley clash heads on a fast break causing both to leave the game and Booker has to get stitches.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker, Beverley clash heads, both leave the game) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker, Beverley clash heads, both leave the game

videos.description: Devin Booker knocks down the jumper giving Phoenix the lead with under 30 seconds remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker gives Suns the lead with jumper) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker gives Suns the lead with jumper

videos.description: Ivica Zubac blocks Cam Payne's layup and Paul George races down the court to put in a layup for a 101-100 Clippers lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zubac's block sets up PG fast-break bucket) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zubac's block sets up PG's fast-break bucket

videos.description: Paul George knocks down the jumper over Jae Crowder giving the Clippers a late lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (PG cashes jumper giving Clippers the lead) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: PG cashes jumper giving Clippers the lead

videos.description: Deandre Ayton describes his game-winning alley-oop and how the last play was drawn up.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Ayton had no clue his game-winning dunk counted) 2021/06/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ayton had no clue his game-winning dunk counted

videos.description: The Suns take a 2-0 lead in the series as they pull off a dramatic 104-103 win over the Clippers after some late-game heroics from Deandre Ayton in the closing moments.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Suns take down Clippers in Game 2 thriller) 2021/06/22 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Suns take down Clippers in Game 2 thriller

videos.description: Monty Williams draws up a play in the Suns' huddle and Deandre Ayton executes it to perfection.

videos.headline: Monty Williams draws up the perfect play

videos.description: Cam Payne joins SVP to discuss the Suns' Game 2 win and what his role is with Chris Paul out.
